The reason I gave this app only 3 stars is mainly because I was expecting 
it to be more hands on. For example it would have been nice to be able to 
select what part of the face should actually be used. One of the filters is 
where a hand is holding a piece of the face that you choose, but you cann...Full ReviewThe reason I gave this app only 3 stars is mainly because I was expecting 
it to be more hands on. For example it would have been nice to be able to 
select what part of the face should actually be used. One of the filters is 
where a hand is holding a piece of the face that you choose, but you cannot 
pick what part of the face us actually getting held which was a bummer to 
start off with. Another one of the filters that I tried out was one that 
looked really cool, it's like the face with the hair was kept with a cool 
filter over it. However, when I tried to use itit didnt erase the 
background at all and just kind of faded. This problem could have been 
fixed if it had let you pick where the edges should be and then add the 
filter. The only thing I really liked was all of the possible fonts. In 
conclusion, if you are looking for a hands on editing app, this is NOT for 
you.
